# Stuffed mushrooms

## Ingredients

- 1 mushroom (portobello or champignon)
- 60g tablespoons of cream cheese (or ricotta)
- 30g grated cheese
- 30g nuts (toasted for tastier result)
- herbs


## Instructions

- Pre-heat oven (225Â° C)
- Crush coarseley the nuts
- Trimm the mushroom 
- Blend the mushroom stems with a hand mixer
- Mix the cream cheese, nuts, blended stems and herbs in a bowl
- Stuff the mushroom cap with the mix
- Sprinkle the grated cheese on top
- Bake it until golden brown
